  <brief_title>Monoclonal Antibodies Elimination in Breast Cancer Patient</brief_title>
  <acronym>PK-MAB</acronym>
  <official_title>Study of the Relative Impact of the Neonatal Fc Receptor (FcRn) and the Therapeutic History on Monoclonal Antibodies Elimination. Proof of the Concept on Patients Treated by Bevacizumab or Trastuzumab in Breast Cancer</official_title>
